   Coverage Defects Repaired in 6.3i
     * For some cases using array element as a clock in FSM detection used to
       give an internal error. This has been fixed now.
     * Enabling of toggle coverage in an optimized design resulted in false
       "part-select out of bounds" error messages from vopt in some cases.
   ______________________________________________________________________

   General Defects Repaired in 6.3i
     * The performance profiler crashed the simulator, producing the error
       message "Internal error! Stack trace within handle_tick". This occurred
       when QuickThreads were used by PLI/VPI/FLI/DPI applications.
     * The simulator would crash if you attempt to restart the simulation after
       a fatal Zero-delay oscillation loop error was reported.
   ______________________________________________________________________

   Mentor Graphics DRs Repaired in 6.3i
     * dts0100383065 - set vsim +nowarn argument in "modelsim.ini".
