     * dts0100510941 - Internal error during vsim due to templated super class
       parameters and the unpacking operator.
     * dts0100512184 - Wrong hold violation with +acc=bmprn.
     * dts0100512188 - Internal error : ../../../src/gencomp.c(2977).
     * dts0100512536 - Segfault when compiling with 6.4 against a file that
       works under 6.3g.
     * dts0100512898  -  Error  tkerror  {couldn't open "/tmp/tmp.html" :
       permission denied} when trying to open online documentation.
     * dts0100516856 - "log -r /*" crashes tool.
     * dts0100517669 - Disable fork disabling process outside it's scope.
     * dts0100518941 - vopt error with mixed Verilog-VHDL signals.
     * dts0100519415 - "-pa_check" vopt option causes vsim crash.
     * dts0100521623 - Internal error: ../../../src/vlog/vgendecl.c(10457) clk
       != NULL.
